window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Collected for the first time anywhere, the nine tales in <i>The Egg and Other Stories</i> highlight Andy Weir's trademark wit and unexpected twists. For the few who have yet to experience <i>The Martian</i>, it's a perfect appetizer. For passionate Weir fans, it's a delicious dessert. </p> <p>Stories included in this audio-exclusive collection are: </p> <p></p> <ul> <li>\"Access\" </li> <li>\"Antihypoxiant\" </li> <li>\"Annie's Day\" </li> <li>\"The Real Deal\" </li> <li>\"Bored World\" </li> <li>\"The Midtown Butcher\" </li> <li>\"Meeting Sarah\" </li> <li>\"The Chef\" </li> <li>\"The Egg\" </li> </ul> <p></p>"; 
